info.name: Mini Breakfast
info.description: Start your day with our delightful Mini Breakfast Platter, offering a variety of South Indian favorites. Enjoy fluffy Pooris paired with a flavorful Poori Masal, a crispy Mini Masala Dosa filled with spiced potato, creamy Pongal, and a sweet and fragrant Kesari. Complemented by three varieties of chutney—coconut, tomato, and mint—and served with savory sambhar and daal,
